<hr class="mb-0" />

<div class="row mb-3">
    <div class="col col-3">
        <div class="card mt-3 border-1 book-details-info-container">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5>
                    Författare:
                    @*foreach (var author in Model.BookAuthors)
                        {
                            author
                        }*@
                </h5>
                <h5>ISBN: @Model.Isbn</h5>
                <h5>Språk: @Model.Language</h5>
                <h5>Utgiven: @Model.PublisherDate</h5>
                <h5>Förlag: @Model.PublisherId</h5>
                <h5>Antal sidor: @Model.TotalPage</h5>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col col-9">
        <div class="card mt-3 border-0">
            <div class="card-body p-0">
                <h2 class="card-title">Beskrivning</h2>
                <p>
                    @Model.Description
                    @*This brief book is an easy-to-digest introduction to the key concepts of web development. Understand the concepts of the web and how they apply to static and dynamic websites. See how HTML and CSS are used to create the bones of the web.
                        Concisely presented through four key concept chapters, Introducing Web Development will enable you to get a clear understanding of how web development works.*@
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>

<hr class="" />

